# AI Image Studio — Environment Variables
#
# This file is for local development reference only.
# No environment variables are required — users provide their
# Google AI Studio API key directly in the app's Settings panel.
#
# Get your free key at: https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
#
# If you want to pre-configure a key for local dev (optional):
# GEMINI_API_KEY=your-gemini-api-key-here
